===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  sodium_crypto_aead_aes256gcm_is_available(): bool~

The return value of this function depends on whether or not the hardware
supports hardware-accelerated AES.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

This function has no parameters.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Returns true if it is safe to encrypt with AES-256-GCM, and false otherwise.


